    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/14612cd3cbd5f1f125997b187aaa5488.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女未姐妹的大哥从小就患有哮喘，导致他之前大部分时间只能静卧在床。现在他的健康状况有所改善后，他尽力通过线上学习弥补那些错过的时光。作为医学研究人员的父母应用从他身上搜集到的特殊数据来发展自己的研究，对医学做出了巨大的贡献。因此他们之前让他多休息，过平静放松的生活缓解症状，以持续提供研究数据，帮助全世界的病患。也正是这对双亲提出了以拥抱来提高免疫力的想法，这让他的生活不再平静。现在每天晚上，他都需要做出选择，到底要抱哪一个妹妹！？面对这突然变化的日常，身为哥哥又会怎么做呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/1265c2c2aee9b65d10f17a4ecc62e0ab.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立绘精美的电子小说，玩家会随着剧情展开体验姐妹之爱和紧紧拥抱的夜晚！精彩纷呈的故事让人着迷，每个妹妹都有自己的性格和故事。做出选择，按自己的想法去塑造一个美好的故事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/72704b5dc70be1d51c83c4ec2d3a8367.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/cf004629a5f387a19f6e4896b5482407.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/84e4c245e7f2df0481061ae8a2726477.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/f6a44ce3332449872d58827bf1c81ce5.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/3c1631d8a6abaae3da92752aafc91644.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155290/extras/b7e8ce469499059d712d94bf082d3def.avif?t=1757736039\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随意自如的拥抱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽你所能拥抱妹妹们吧！通过点击可以控制拥抱的时间和力度，以获得天然分泌的内啡肽！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自选妹妹</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以拥抱任意一个妹妹！选择你最想拥抱，最想用满怀的爱去包容的那个妹妹吧！</p>",
